Perry Drug Stores Inc said DonaldFox has resigned from the board of directors, effectiveimmediately.    Fox, a board director since 1971, said he was resigningbecause of new business interests, the company reported. Foxleft Perry as president and chief operating officer in Januaryand was recently appointed president of Beauty Brands Group, adistributor based in Southfield, Mich., the company said. Reuter&#3;